This is the Camel route:

```java
fromF("timer:%s?period=%d", tagGroupName, interval)
        .routeId(tagGroupName)
        .process(exchange -> {
            Map<String, Object> result = tagReaderService.directRead(tagGroupTriggerData.getHost(),
                    tagGroupTriggerData.getPort(),
